WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.659
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.660 --> 00:01:01.474
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.475 --> 00:01:03.195
=Episode 2=

00:01:04.259 --> 00:01:05.780
You bit me! Why you little...

00:01:09.460 --> 00:01:10.939
I was going to
spare you the humiliation.

00:01:10.940 --> 00:01:12.136
But since you insist,

00:01:12.137 --> 00:01:13.258
I'll make sure you

00:01:13.259 --> 00:01:15.140
learn what living hell really means.

00:01:15.419 --> 00:01:16.379
Sir.

00:01:16.499 --> 00:01:17.939
Earlier,

00:01:17.940 --> 00:01:19.539
I was in the wrong.

00:01:22.139 --> 00:01:24.019
A spring night is worth a thousand gold.

00:01:26.419 --> 00:01:27.379
Why not

00:01:28.259 --> 00:01:30.299
let me serve you properly?

00:01:33.699 --> 00:01:35.420
Sir, they've shown themselves.

00:01:38.820 --> 00:01:41.579
Good. Take them alive.

00:02:07.037 --> 00:02:09.207
Official Gu!

00:02:22.825 --> 00:02:26.432
笙ｪEven if I drift
within a darkened whirl笙ｪ

00:02:26.712 --> 00:02:30.761
笙ｪKindred souls
meet the light and become one笙ｪ

00:02:30.762 --> 00:02:38.574
笙ｪSo many chapters,
every wound remembered笙ｪ

00:02:38.575 --> 00:02:42.299
笙ｪBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain笙ｪ

00:02:42.300 --> 00:02:45.932
笙ｪThe night runs deep like watching eyes笙ｪ

00:02:46.740 --> 00:02:48.180
Official Gu.

00:02:49.539 --> 00:02:51.180
I feel awful.

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:53.580
You've been drugged.

00:02:55.137 --> 00:02:57.811
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:02:57.812 --> 00:02:59.949
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:02:59.950 --> 00:03:03.570
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:10.811
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:03:10.812 --> 00:03:12.180
So thirsty...

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:15.279
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:19.279
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:22.139
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:03:22.140 --> 00:03:23.500
Get some clothes.

00:03:23.819 --> 00:03:24.599
Yes.

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:27.024
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:03:27.025 --> 00:03:29.745
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:03:38.939 --> 00:03:40.379
Stop drinking.

00:03:46.619 --> 00:03:48.580
You may be a womanizer,

00:03:49.020 --> 00:03:51.419
but you're quite the looker.

00:03:51.779 --> 00:03:54.099
Let me take a closer look.

00:03:54.850 --> 00:03:58.086
笙ｪCarrying the weight of hatred笙ｪ

00:03:58.087 --> 00:04:01.907
笙ｪBurying every trace of love笙ｪ

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:06.586
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

00:04:06.587 --> 00:04:10.186
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

00:04:10.187 --> 00:04:14.658
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and we stand side by side笙ｪ

00:04:14.659 --> 00:04:15.961
Always so cruel to yourself...

00:04:15.962 --> 00:04:18.982
笙ｪSide by side we walk on笙ｪ

00:04:19.193 --> 00:04:21.900
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:04:21.937 --> 00:04:24.086
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:04:24.087 --> 00:04:27.574
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:04:27.575 --> 00:04:35.435
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:04:37.750 --> 00:04:40.682
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:04:49.659 --> 00:04:51.499
If you want to keep that hand,

00:04:52.299 --> 00:04:53.499
then bear with it.

00:05:24.659 --> 00:05:26.539
Thank you, Gu Chengye.

00:05:27.500 --> 00:05:29.132
This is the last time I'm helping you.

00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:33.619
Sir, your...

00:05:44.950 --> 00:05:46.298
I'll step out for a moment.

00:05:46.299 --> 00:05:47.995
Get changed and wait for me.

00:05:51.387 --> 00:05:53.386
Fresh clothes are here, Miss Song.

00:05:55.060 --> 00:05:56.579
(This place is full of danger.)

00:05:56.580 --> 00:05:57.774
(If I want to stay alive,)

00:05:57.775 --> 00:05:59.334
(I need to hold on to Gu Chengye.)

00:05:59.335 --> 00:06:01.770
(Imperial Guard.)

00:06:07.940 --> 00:06:10.340
It wasn't easy luring you out.

00:06:11.140 --> 00:06:12.299
Talk.

00:06:12.739 --> 00:06:14.179
What's your organization called?

00:06:20.060 --> 00:06:22.299
I hear your ranks are
tightly disciplined.

00:06:24.859 --> 00:06:25.979
Perfect.

00:06:26.339 --> 00:06:27.418
We happen to have

00:06:27.419 --> 00:06:28.820
a few little toys ourselves.

00:06:46.637 --> 00:06:48.460
Sir, Miss Song requests an audience.

00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:50.900
What is she doing here?

00:06:52.380 --> 00:06:53.299
I'm not seeing her.

00:06:55.339 --> 00:06:56.260
Wait.

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:03.940
Have her wait.

00:07:04.060 --> 00:07:05.059
Yes, sir.

00:07:19.060 --> 00:07:20.260
Official Gu.

00:07:24.339 --> 00:07:26.820
I didn't expect
the former courtesan queen

00:07:27.539 --> 00:07:30.139
to have a habit of barging
into a man's bedchamber.

00:07:30.140 --> 00:07:33.020
I came to discuss something important.

00:07:35.299 --> 00:07:38.145
You're the one
who lacks a gentleman's virtue.

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:45.579
Go on.

00:07:46.979 --> 00:07:49.379
To repay you for all your care,

00:07:49.380 --> 00:07:51.778
I personally made this sachet for you.

00:07:51.779 --> 00:07:54.139
It's filled with sleep-aiding herbs.

00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:56.900
I stayed up
the whole night to finish it.

00:08:04.140 --> 00:08:07.220
A new piece from Linglong Workshop,
the finest embroidery house.

00:08:07.620 --> 00:08:09.140
Exquisite craftsmanship.

00:08:15.299 --> 00:08:17.778
I didn't expect Official Gu
to know Linglong Workshop so well.

00:08:17.779 --> 00:08:19.940
Spare me the useless tricks.

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:22.059
State your purpose.

00:08:32.687 --> 00:08:33.767
Official Gu.

00:08:39.299 --> 00:08:41.779
You've helped me time and again.

00:08:41.819 --> 00:08:43.859
I can't be ungrateful.

00:08:44.459 --> 00:08:45.818
I came today

00:08:45.819 --> 00:08:48.820
to seek your protection.

00:08:52.819 --> 00:08:53.979
By all due reasons,

00:08:53.980 --> 00:08:55.580
you ought to protect me.

00:08:55.980 --> 00:08:57.460
What makes you think

00:08:57.699 --> 00:08:59.099
I would?

00:08:59.237 --> 00:09:01.220
(You say one thing, mean another.)

00:09:04.900 --> 00:09:06.379
You're investigating

00:09:06.380 --> 00:09:08.220
an organization marked by tattoos.

00:09:13.699 --> 00:09:15.460
So, you haven't lost your memory.

00:09:15.539 --> 00:09:16.820
I did lose it.

00:09:18.579 --> 00:09:20.379
But from certain clues,

00:09:20.380 --> 00:09:21.700
I deduced

00:09:22.340 --> 00:09:24.379
that you're investigating

00:09:24.380 --> 00:09:26.899
a mysterious group
tied to Huanyue House.

00:09:27.539 --> 00:09:28.859
And before this,

00:09:28.939 --> 00:09:31.259
I was your most trusted informant.

00:09:32.179 --> 00:09:33.379
On the Lantern Festival,

00:09:33.380 --> 00:09:34.739
I was attacked,

00:09:34.740 --> 00:09:35.698
pushed from a building,

00:09:35.699 --> 00:09:36.899
and lost my memory.

00:09:36.980 --> 00:09:37.859
That's why

00:09:38.059 --> 00:09:39.940
you grew suspicious of me,

00:09:40.380 --> 00:09:42.540
yet couldn't bring yourself to act.

00:09:43.299 --> 00:09:44.499
Tell me,

00:09:44.819 --> 00:09:46.540
did I get anything wrong?

00:09:55.825 --> 00:09:57.139
You are clever.

00:09:57.900 --> 00:09:59.540
But, Song Zhiyun,

00:10:00.500 --> 00:10:02.653
as far as I'm concerned,

00:10:04.620 --> 00:10:06.460
you're a discarded piece.

00:10:09.939 --> 00:10:10.778
Official Gu,

00:10:10.779 --> 00:10:12.099
I've already died once.

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:13.340
I'm not who I used to be.

00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:15.660
Please, trust me again.

00:10:15.900 --> 00:10:17.460
If you're willing to protect me,

00:10:17.500 --> 00:10:19.619
I'll do everything I can
to help you solve this case.

00:10:19.620 --> 00:10:21.139
I won't let you lose.

00:10:26.380 --> 00:10:27.580
Wei Cheng.

00:10:29.687 --> 00:10:30.660
Sir.

00:10:31.100 --> 00:10:32.379
How is

00:10:33.459 --> 00:10:34.739
our respected guest?

00:10:34.939 --> 00:10:36.940
He's confessed to everything.

00:10:36.950 --> 00:10:38.460
But barely breathing.

00:10:40.020 --> 00:10:41.139
Perfect.

00:10:41.419 --> 00:10:42.940
Then let Miss Song

00:10:43.980 --> 00:10:45.940
meet her old friend.

00:10:54.179 --> 00:10:55.899
The laws of the Great Song are strict.

00:10:55.900 --> 00:10:58.619
The Imperial Guard's punishments
are far more elaborate.

00:10:58.939 --> 00:11:00.379
You're just a fragile woman,

00:11:01.179 --> 00:11:04.300
yet you keep talking about investigating
and cooperation.

00:11:06.020 --> 00:11:08.619
Forget whether you could
endure even a fraction of it.

00:11:08.825 --> 00:11:10.660
I doubt you'd even dare

00:11:11.620 --> 00:11:12.979
to carry out the torture.

00:11:20.380 --> 00:11:22.019
You want the truth?

00:11:22.380 --> 00:11:23.739
Show me your resolve.

00:11:32.699 --> 00:11:35.499
Whether you're Song Zhiyun or Liu Ruyan,

00:11:35.620 --> 00:11:38.420
it seems you've forgotten
what we're up against.

00:11:38.620 --> 00:11:40.060
What we face

00:11:40.939 --> 00:11:42.779
is an endless hell.

00:11:43.939 --> 00:11:45.259
If you want to work with me,

00:11:45.819 --> 00:11:47.220
this blade

00:11:48.620 --> 00:11:50.300
must be drawn.

00:12:27.419 --> 00:12:28.499
Go on.

00:12:28.819 --> 00:12:30.619
You cursed woman.

00:12:30.620 --> 00:12:32.580
If you've got the guts, kill me.

00:12:48.539 --> 00:12:49.580
As expected.

00:12:49.939 --> 00:12:51.658
All talk.

00:12:51.659 --> 00:12:53.139
Timid as a rat.

00:12:53.179 --> 00:12:54.180
Someone like you

00:12:54.620 --> 00:12:56.060
can never be trusted.

00:12:56.819 --> 00:12:58.139
You filthy woman.

00:12:58.260 --> 00:12:59.619
Falling into your hands

00:12:59.620 --> 00:13:01.019
is my bad luck.

00:13:01.220 --> 00:13:02.940
We won't let you off.

00:13:03.539 --> 00:13:04.778
We'll make sure you

00:13:04.779 --> 00:13:06.058
are used by every man

00:13:06.059 --> 00:13:07.899
and wish you were dead.

00:13:37.779 --> 00:13:38.859
So?

00:13:40.260 --> 00:13:41.580
Is that enough?

00:13:44.699 --> 00:13:46.099
Am I qualified now

00:13:47.659 --> 00:13:49.259
to be your blade?